rules: .nav-menu-content[data-state="open"] { animation: 0.25s ease 0s 1 normal none running scaleIn; }
.nav-menu-content[data-state="closed"] { animation: 0.25s ease 0s 1 normal none running scaleOut; }
.nav-menu-content[data-motion="from-start"] { animation: 0.25s ease 0s 1 normal none running enterFromLeft; }
.nav-menu-content[data-motion="from-end"] { animation: 0.25s ease 0s 1 normal none running enterFromRight; }
.nav-menu-content[data-motion="to-start"] { animation: 0.25s ease 0s 1 normal none running exitToLeft; }
.nav-menu-content[data-motion="to-end"] { animation: 0.25s ease 0s 1 normal none running exitToRight; }

pre { margin-block: calc(var(--spacing)*4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border-style: var(--tw-border-style); border-width: 1px; border-color: var(--color-base-800); padding: calc(var(--spacing)*4); font-family: var(--font-geist-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); --tw-leading: calc(var(--spacing)*6); line-height: calc(var(--spacing)*6); overflow-x: auto; }
pre[data-theme="light"] { border-color: var(--color-base-300); background-color: var(--color-light-base-primary); color: var(--color-dark-base-primary); }
code { font-family: var(--font-geist-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: var(--tw-leading,var(--text-sm--line-height)); }

:not(pre) > code { border-style: var(--tw-border-style); border-width: 1px; border-color: var(--color-base-400); background-color: var(--color-base-600); padding-inline: calc(var(--spacing)*1); font-size: var(--text-xs); line-height: var(--tw-leading,var(--text-xs--line-height)); color: var(--color-light-base-secondary); border-radius: 0.25rem; padding-block: 1px; }

pre [data-highlighted-line] { margin-left: calc(var(--spacing)*-4); border-left: 2px var(--tw-border-style) var(--color-accent-100); padding-right: calc(var(--spacing)*4); padding-left: calc(var(--spacing)*2); background-color: rgba(239, 111, 46, 0.1); }
